# name: test_ms_test_help_block
  '''
  usage: ms-test.py [-h] [--url URL] [--section SECTION] [--json]
                    [--destructive] [--self-improve] [--apply]
                    [--model {opus,sonnet,haiku}] [--analyze-tests] [--trend]
  
  Mediastack comprehensive test suite
  
  options:
    -h, --help            show this help message and exit
    --url URL             API base URL
    --section SECTION     Run only these sections (e.g. A,B,F,M,N)
    --json                Machine-readable JSON output
    --destructive         Include tests that modify data (install, wizard, etc.)
    --self-improve        Generate improvements via AI based on run history
    --apply               Apply self-improvements to ms-test.py (use with
                          --self-improve)
    --model {opus,sonnet,haiku}
                          AI model for --self-improve (default: sonnet)
    --analyze-tests       Analyze existing pytest suite for quality and gaps
    --trend               Show pass/fail trends from run history
  
  '''
# ---
# name: test_ms_update_help_banner
  '''
  Usage: sudo ms-update [--full] [--tests]
    (no flags)  Standard update with smart recommendations
    --full      Update + run ALL test scripts immediately
    --tests     Skip update, run test scripts only
  
  '''
# ---
